asset.hookText: Two-time welterweight champ, Paul Williams, talks about what he likes best about boxing and how he feels about being dubbed the most feared fighter in boxing.  Williams meets Kermit Cintron in a junior middleweight showdown on World Championship Boxing, Saturday, May 8th, live on HBO.
